headline: Should Mounting Cocoa Costs and Profit Concerns Require Action From Mondelez International (MDLZ) Investors?
summary: Mondelez International is set to announce its third-quarter results after the market closes on October 28, with analysts anticipating a significant decrease in adjusted profit per share compared to the prior year, primarily due to elevated cocoa prices and increased raw material costs. While some international markets are delivering strong revenue growth, the company faces mounting challenges in North and Latin America alongside broader analyst concerns about profitability, which have...

headline: NHLPA Goals & Dreams and OREO Proudly Deliver $200,000 in Equipment to Deserving Hockey Communities Across Canada
summary: The National Hockey League Players' Association (NHLPA) and OREO proudly announce the grant recipients of the inaugural OREO Stay Playful For All program, providing $200,000 in hockey equipment from OREO and NHLPA Goals & Dreams to youth hockey organizations across Canada. Designed to enhance the accessibility of grassroots hockey among youth in Canada, the program helps invigorate local communities, keep the sport inclusive, and nurture the next generation of hockey players.
